      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior looks great overall, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a solid service history, making it a reliable and attractive choice for its next owner.",
