    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, a few small door dings, and some minor paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and some staining on the carpets, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, but the brakes will likely need service soon and the tires have about 30% tread life remaining. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind some aesthetic imperfections and upcoming routine maintenance.",
      "price": 20500.0,
